<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:9:72">
	<strong>Need Approval to Volunteer?&nbsp;</strong>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:10:17">
	Some of our volunteer opportunities require a specific application, a&nbsp;background check, and Safe From Harm Training.&nbsp;
</p>
<ol style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:11:53">
	<li>Fill out our <a href="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uss-cache.salvationarmy.org/cfeeba3b-482b-41e5-a946-9c8a6954dec3_2023+VOLUNTEER+APPLICATION+-+PDF+Edit.pdf">Volunteer Application</a> or <a href="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uss-cache.salvationarmy.org/2149300e-0851-40fb-add1-882838baa3c2_Volunteer+Application+for+Children.pdf">Volunteer Application for Working with Children</a> </li>
	<li>Complete the Background Check (The link will be sent to your email address provided on the application)</li>
	<li>Participate in Safe from Harm Training (Our Volunteer Coordinator will contact you once all the forms are completed and approved!)</li>
</ol>
